="superscript">ten</hi></date> an den <rs ref="#pmb39975" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Gardasee</hi></rs>.<note type="textConst" xml:id="TL1901-09-06_01_Hofmannsthal_AS-1h">quer am linken Rand</note></p></postscript></div></body></text></TEI>